================================================================================

This project is a clean-room reimplementation. It is NOT affiliated with,
endorsed by, or derived from the original game's source code.

The original game "Lander" (1987) for the Acorn Archimedes is the work of
David Braben and remains his copyright.

The reverse-engineered, annotated source code published at
https://lander.bbcelite.com is the work of Mark Moxon and remains his
copyright. No code, comments, constants, or asset files from that project
are included or copied in this repository. The site was used solely as a
behavioral specification: gameplay mechanics, formulas, and architectural
notes — none of which are themselves protected by copyright.

If you want to read or build the original game's reverse-engineered source,
visit https://lander.bbcelite.com. We strongly recommend it.
